requirements.term:
Subjects to be covered in the entrance interview: 

**•** Explain what interests you about the CAM programme; 

**•** Knowledge about Estonia as a (future) place of study; 

**•** Knowledge about Tartu relating to the Applicant’s hobbies and interests (options for leisure activities you find interesting); 

**•** Describe your career prospects and aspirations; 

**•** Questions to test your analytical and problem-solving skills. 

Test is online and duration of the test is 20-30 minutes

