requirements.term:
The application system DreamApply Estonia opens on the 2nd of January. The application closes on the 30th of April for all candidates. If you have any questions please contact admissions@eava.ee. 

The following documents must be submitted electronically via DreamApply by the application deadline: 

**•** online application; 

**•** motivation letter; 

**•** curriculum vitae (CV); 

**•** a copy of an identity document (passport or ID card); 

**•** official certified copy of the secondary school certificate; 

**•** document certifying English language proficiency of at least B2 level; 

**•** document certifying: 
  - CPL(A) or CPL(H) licence with ATPL theory endorsement or 
  - ATPL(A) or ATPL(H) licence or 
  - training documentation that proves passing of CPL(A) or CPL (H) training with ATPL theory. 

**•** confirmation/receipt of application fee (50 €). 

Documents in any other language than English and Estonian must be submitted upon request along with an Estonian or English translation, which must be certified by the issuer of the document, a sworn translator or a notary.

